d by WPTF see sec 3.1.3\nPRR 1359 Changes to section 6.6.5 due to Summer ... PRR 1360 Added new sections in Market Operations \nBPM due to the Summer Readiness initiative related to ... 68 1278 10/28/2020 PRR 1278 The ISO has implemented several \nimprovements to the Non-Generator Resource (NGR) Model in the day-ahead and real-time market. The PRR \ndocument provides detailed information regarding the ... are documented in the Business Requirement \nSpecification, and the impacts to Market Operation due ... 64 1210 01/29/2020 PRR1210 Provide an additional method for satisfying the Regulation recertification requirement in the event of \na resource’s failure to meet the minimum performance ... years back, we moved the HASP start-up timeline to \n71.5 minutes before the trading hour. This is an update ... Version PRR Date Description\n62 1167, 1162 09/09/2019 PRR1167 This revision is based on the Tariff clarification amendment filling section 42.1.5 to state \nthat the CAISO may also enter into real-time contracts for unloaded resource"
